Bindery is the business website for Dreaming Mind Studio, a hand book bindery.

It's a purpose built CMS that builds galleries, news feeds, workshop descriptions and other presentations.
The most basic unit of information is an Image.
An Image hasMany Content so it can be described in various ways.
Content hasAndBelongsToMany Collections through ContentCollection

This structure forces a picture-based approach to presenting information

For information: Don Drake, ddrake@dreamingmind.com
